tourBios.carHigh:
2015: Earned PGA TOUR Latinoamérica status with a T6 finish at the Developmental Series Final in Ecuador in January… Made the cut in two of four starts on PGA TOUR Latinoamérica, with a T49 at the Mazatlán Open as his best… Closed the year with a T7 at the Developmental Series Final in Ecuador to earn back his Latinoamérica Tour card for the 2016 season.

2014: Only cut made in two starts on PGA TOUR Latinoamérica was a T32 finish at the Arturo Calle Colombia Open… Won the Abierto Opita de Golf on the Colombian Tour.

2013: Finished T12 at the Arturo Calle Colombia Open in Pereira on his only cut made in two starts on PGA TOUR Latinoamérica… Won the III Abierto del Ruitoque CC on the Colombian Tour.

2012: Missed the cut at the 65 Arturo Calle Colombia Open on his only start of the PGA TOUR Latinoamérica inaugural season.

2011: Finished T16 at the Barranquilla Colombia Championship, an event co-sanctioned by the Tour de las Américas and PGA TOUR Canada.

2010: Finished T45 at the Abierto Internacional II Copa Antioquia, an event co-sanctioned by the Tour de las Américas, the European Challenge Tour and PGA TOUR Canada.
tourBios.exmtStatus: Exempt - Finished 6-10 at 2015 Dev Series Final (exempt to midseason reshuffle)

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Latinoameri was T12th in 2013 at the 66 Arturo Calle Colombian Open Presentado por Diners Club.
